videos.description: Virginia Tech defensive lineman Houshun Gaines hammers William & Mary quarterback Shon Mitchell for the sack. Mitchell fumbles the ball and the Hokies recover.
videos.headline: Hokies go on offense after recovering fumble

videos.description: Virginia Tech capitalizes on a turnover and call running back Steven Peoples' number to punch in a 6-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: VT punches in rush TD

videos.description: Virginia Tech WR Damon Hazelton leaves a Tribe defender in the dust for a beautiful 39-yard touchdown catch from QB Josh Jackson.
videos.headline: Hokies WR smokes defender for 39-yard TD

videos.description: Hokies offensive linemen give a powerful second effort to lunge QB Josh Jackson into the end zone for an 8-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: VT O-Line muscles QB in for bizarre TD

videos.description: William & Mary quarterback Shon Mitchell connects with tight end Nick Muse for a long 71-yard gain to set up a Nate Evans 4-yard rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Tribe 71-yard catch-and-run sets up rush TD

videos.description: Virginia Tech running back Steven Peoples bulldozes his way into the end zone for his second rushing touchdown of the game, capping off an 81-yard drive for the Hokies.
videos.headline: Hokies RB pounds in 2nd TD of game

videos.description: Virginia Tech running back Deshawn MClease powers his way in for a 1-yard TD to put the Hokies up 38-7 before halftime.
videos.headline: Hokies balloon lead with rush TD

videos.description: Hokies running back Terius Wheatley dives in for a 1-yard TD, Virginia Tech's fifth rushing touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: VT converts 5th rush TD of game

videos.description: William & Mary WR DeVonte Dedmon turns a bubble screen into a 59-yard touchdown from  Shon Mitchell.
videos.headline: W&M WR turns on jets for 59-yard TD

videos.description: Virginia Tech quarterback Ryan Willis pounds in a keeper from seven yards out for another Hokies rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Hokies pile on lead with 7-yard rush TD
